ve.org/web/20200523222739/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252392 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和北泽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252389 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2020-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516162750/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252389 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252393 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-24 |archive-date=2020-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200516205607/http://www.ynszxc.net/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=252393 |dead-url=no }}</ref>)分布(白碧波2010:118)。

[[因远镇|因远镇]]梭比社群被[[白宏语|白宏语]]和豪尼语社群包围(白碧波2010)。

梭比语也在[[新平彝族傣族自治县|新平彝族傣族自治县]](在[[建兴乡_(新平县)|建兴乡]]梅子箐和[[复兴乡|复兴乡]]大寨)有分布。<ref>新平县志(1993:106, 118)</ref>

